<U+0001F4CD>Ethermore characters start true neutral.

Each choice is permanent. Each has a consequence on who you are.

Little by little, you will move across the moral compass towards or away from good/evil and order/chaos.

Certain choices are only available to polarised moralities.

Just a creative shoutout to @ParallelNFT 
Turning the magic of tabletop/card/RP games into blockchain games is hard and requires a mix of vision/execution. 

You have Ethermores support from your blockchain game buddies.  <U+0001F44C>

Once a choice is made in Ethermore, it is set. 
No character can go around again. 
Decisions have consequences.
Different characters traits present different options.
